videos.description: Syracuse holds a moment of silence for Jorge Jimenez before its game against Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Syracuse holds moment of silence for Jorge Jimenez) 2019/2/23

videos.headline: Syracuse holds moment of silence for Jorge Jimenez

videos.description: During a commercial break, a Syracuse fan delights the crowd with his crazy dancing.
videos.headline: Syracuse fan delights the crowd with his dancing

videos.description: Elijah Hughes runs the length of the court to block Cam Reddish's breakaway dunk.
videos.headline: Hughes blocks Reddish's breakaway dunk

videos.description: RJ Barrett has 17 points at halftime, but currently it's not enough as Syracuse leads No. 1 Duke 34-29 at halftime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Cuse leads Duke by 5 at half) 2019/2/23 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Cuse leads Duke by 5 at half

videos.description: Marek Dolezaj finds a wide-open Elijah Hughes as Hughes throws down the big slam dunk.
videos.headline: Hughes throws down two-handed slam

videos.description: RJ Barrett fakes out his defender off the pass and hits the wide open 3-pointer for Duke.
videos.headline: Barrett fakes out defender, hits wide-open 3

videos.description: Alex O'Connell and RJ Barrett score on back-to-back dunks as Duke extends begins to pull away from Syracuse in the second half.
videos.headline: Duke's back-to-back dunks extend lead

videos.description: Jim Boeheim issues a public apology to the family of Jorge Jimenez, who was killed when he was struck by a car driven by Boeheim, saying, "This is something that will be with me for the rest of my life."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Boeheim delivers apology to Jimenez family after loss) 2019/2/23

videos.headline: Boeheim delivers apology to Jimenez's family after loss

videos.description: RJ Barrett has nothing but praise for his teammates as Duke gets revenge vs. Syracuse at the Carrier Dome Saturday night.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Barrett credits success to teammates in win vs. Cuse) 2019/2/23

videos.headline: Barrett credits success to teammates in win vs. Cuse

videos.description: Duke head coach Mike Krzyzewski says that there has been no talk of shutting phenom Zion Williamson down after his mild knee sprain vs. North Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Coach K: ‘We would never play a kid who's not ready’) 2019/2/23

videos.headline: Coach K: 'We would never play a kid who's not ready'
